Problem Statement :
                    There is a circular track of length M consisting of M checkpoints and M bidirectional roads such 
                    that each road has a length of 1 unit.
                    Chef is currently at checkpoint A and wants to reach checkpoint B. Find the minimum length of the road he needs to travel
                    
Problem Code :   LOOP 
